title: Dog Hilariously Voices His Opinion When Girl Plays Flute
text:
Dog Hilariously Voices His Opinion When Girl Plays Flute   
This dog either doesn’t appreciate musical talent or doesn’t like his nap being interrupted by his little human’s flute practice. In this funny clip, the girl is playing the flute with her dog laying on the floor behind her. 
But as soon as she starts playing, the dog lets out a deep, hysterical howl. She continues to try and play only for the dog to respond even more dramatically! 
I’m not convinced that he’s actually critiquing her as much as singing along! What do you think? One thing for sure, he got me and his family laughing! 
Share this cute   family.
